l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚係卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e980a4b68694c2c1821d9f9567e6c9840dc198a9","tid":658870,"uid":77705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"又小弟又小妹<br />\n你個fd係男定女啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ffcc250473e54312bd9ce19faed6b8eba66673","tid":658870,"uid":22876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"如果Fresh Grad一畢業就入到EO<br />\n其實真係外邊冇乜工比到你<br />\n即使MT GT完咗program俾個AM你做<br />\n即使間公司幾大或者你幾跑到數都好<br />\n喺五萬個阻力好大好大 <br />\n<br />\n但EO你講緊去到35歲已經七八皮<br />\n可上邊話齋<br />\n其實已經係COO CFO CMO個價錢黎<br />\n私人工來講呢啲位仲論資排輩個政府"},{"pid":"0ec68660b00b958eb2fa5b8caffb6d2cbf83dc66","tid":658870,"uid":89313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e980a4b68694c2c1821d9f9567e6c9840dc198a9","tid":658870,"uid":77705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"又小弟又小妹<br />\n你個fd係男定女啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"篇文上網抄ga,但情況同我fd一樣，唔好理依啲la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9a31c389f7693b02583fd6cca8eba4fce0c93c","tid":658870,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"SF Express好19你又知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea7a066821b650acac4da2930a5085bc4ab94c4","tid":658870,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"BTW，睇你個人有無大志同信心，有大志對自己有信心梗係唔入政府啦"},{"pid":"fe5fdffd873f628e5e025ea4075546456233f274","tid":658870,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:03:48.000Z","